{
  "info": {
    "name": "M2 Backend",
    "description": "M2 Master's registration API. Run Login first — tokens are auto-saved. All protected requests use Bearer auth.\n\n## Workflow notes\n\n**Auth**\n1. Login (email + password) → tokens saved automatically\n2. Token Refresh when access_token expires\n3. Me → current user + registration status\n\n**Admin setup**\n1. Login as admin (superuser)\n2. Create User → for students (email, password, full_name)\n3. Create Teacher → for teachers (email, password, full_name, title, department, is_supervisor)\n\n**Student registration**\n1. Admin creates user OR user registers\n2. Login as student\n3. GET state → get current_step + question\n4. POST answer (repeat) → body key = question.question_key\n5. POST submit when question_type = submit → status SUBMITTED (awaiting coordinator)\n\n**Coordinator – registration verification**\n1. Login as coordinator (Person must be MajorCoordinator for a major)\n2. List Pending → sessions with status SUBMITTED for their major(s)\n3. Accept or Reject (session_id in path)\n4. Accept → status ACCEPTED, profiles/experiences created; Reject → session deleted\n\n**Coordinator – course assignment**\n1. Login as coordinator\n2. List Offerings → course offerings for programs in their major(s) (Program.major must be set)\n3. List Teachers → all teachers (for dropdown)\n4. List Students → students in their major(s); List Cohorts → cohorts for their major(s)\n5. Assign Teacher → POST offering_id in path, teacher_id (person_id) in body\n\n**Teacher**\n1. Login as teacher (assigned to offerings)\n2. List Course Students → GET teacher/courses/<offering_id>/students/",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{access_token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {"key": "base_url", "value": "http://localhost:8000"},
    {"key": "email", "value": "test@example.com"},
    {"key": "password", "value": "testpass123"},
    {"key": "access_token", "value": ""},
    {"key": "refresh_token", "value": ""}
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Admin",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Create User",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"student@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"TempPass123\",\n  \"full_name\": \"John Doe\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/admin/users/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "admin", "users", ""]
            },
            "description": "Admin only. Creates User + Person with email and temp password. Login as admin first."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Create Teacher",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"teacher@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"TempPass123\",\n  \"full_name\": \"Dr. Smith\",\n  \"title\": \"Professor\",\n  \"department\": \"CS\",\n  \"is_supervisor\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/admin/teachers/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "admin", "teachers", ""]
            },
            "description": "Admin only. Creates User + Person + TeacherProfile. Teacher can be assigned to courses by coordinator."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login", ""]
            },
            "description": "Login with email + password. Returns access_token and refresh_token. Use access_token in Authorization header for protected endpoints.",
            "event": [
              {
                "listen": "test",
                "script": {
                  "exec": [
                    "if (pm.response.code !== 200) return;",
                    "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                    "if (jsonData.access_token) {",
                    "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access_token);",
                    "    try { pm.environment.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access_token); } catch (e) {}",
                    "}",
                    "if (jsonData.refresh_token) {",
                    "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"refresh_token\", jsonData.refresh_token);",
                    "    try { pm.environment.set(\"refresh_token\", jsonData.refresh_token); } catch (e) {}",
                    "}"
                  ],
                  "type": "text/javascript"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Token Refresh",
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refresh_token}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/token/refresh/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "token", "refresh", ""]
            },
            "description": "Refresh access token using refresh_token.",
            "event": [
              {
                "listen": "test",
                "script": {
                  "exec": [
                    "if (pm.response.code !== 200) return;",
                    "var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
                    "if (jsonData.access) {",
                    "    pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access);",
                    "    try { pm.environment.set(\"access_token\", jsonData.access); } catch (e) {}",
                    "}"
                  ],
                  "type": "text/javascript"
                }
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/me/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "me", ""]
            },
            "description": "Requires JWT. Returns current user, registration_complete, current_step, roles (student, teacher, coordinator, alumni), and role-based profile (full_name, enrollments, courses, taught_courses, coordinated_majors, etc.)."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Registration",
      "description": "Question flow: 1) GET state → use response.question (question_key, question_type, label, options/fields) to render the form. 2) POST answer with body key = question.question_key. 3) Response includes question for the next step; repeat until question.question_type is \"submit\". 4) POST submit with {} to finish. Validation: major_id must be an existing Major id; institution_name must match an existing Institution name.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Get Registration State",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/state/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "state", ""]
            },
            "description": "Requires auth. Returns current_step, payload, and question (question_key, question_type, label, options or fields) for the current step. Use question to render the form (yes_no, select, object, submit, etc.)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q1: Student Path",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"finished_master\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            },
            "description": "Body key must match question.question_key. Response includes question for next step (e.g. student_data object with fields)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q1: Alumni Path",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"finished_master\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Collect Student Data",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"student_data\": {\n    \"major_id\": 1,\n    \"student_number\": \"M2-2024-001\",\n    \"cohort_year\": \"2024\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q2 Internship: Yes",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"has_internship\": true,\n  \"internship_data\": {\n    \"institution_name\": \"Sorbonne University\",\n    \"department\": \"Research Lab\",\n    \"country\": \"France\",\n    \"start_date\": \"2024-01-01\",\n    \"end_date\": \"2024-06-30\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q2 Internship: No",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"has_internship\": false\n}"},
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q2 Internship Alumni: No",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"had_internship\": false\n}"},
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q3 PhD: Yes",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"is_phd_student\": true,\n  \"phd_data\": {\n    \"institution_name\": \"Sorbonne University\",\n    \"field\": \"Machine Learning\",\n    \"lab_name\": \"AI Lab\",\n    \"start_date\": \"2024-09-01\",\n    \"end_date\": null\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q3 PhD: No",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"is_phd_student\": false\n}"},
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q4 Work: Yes",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"is_working\": true,\n  \"work_data\": {\n    \"institution_name\": \"Sorbonne University\",\n    \"title\": \"Data Scientist\",\n    \"country\": \"France\",\n    \"start_date\": \"2024-01-01\",\n    \"end_date\": null\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Answer - Q4 Work: No",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"is_working\": false\n}"},
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Submit Registration",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{}"},
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/submit/",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "submit", ""]
            },
            "description": "Call when current_step is SUBMIT or question.question_type is \"submit\". Sets status to SUBMITTED (awaiting major coordinator approval). registration_complete is true only after coordinator accepts."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Programs Coordinator",
      "description": "Coordinator manages course offerings for their major(s): list offerings, list teachers, assign teacher to offering.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Offerings",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/programs/coordinator/offerings/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "programs", "coordinator", "offerings", ""]},
            "description": "Returns course offerings for programs in coordinator's major(s). Programs must have major set."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Teachers",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/programs/coordinator/teachers/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "programs", "coordinator", "teachers", ""]},
            "description": "Returns all teachers (for dropdown when assigning)."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Students",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/programs/coordinator/students/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "programs", "coordinator", "students", ""]},
            "description": "Returns students enrolled in coordinator's major(s). Response: { students: [{ person_id, full_name, email, student_number, enrollment_id, cohort_id, cohort_academic_year, major_id, major_code, enrollment_status }] }."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "List Cohorts",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/programs/coordinator/cohorts/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "programs", "coordinator", "cohorts", ""]},
            "description": "Returns cohorts for programs in coordinator's major(s). Response: { cohorts: [{ id, academic_year, program_id, program_name, major_id, major_code }] }."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Assign Teacher",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"teacher_id\": 1\n}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/programs/coordinator/offerings/1/assign/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "programs", "coordinator", "offerings", "1", "assign", ""]},
            "description": "POST with offering_id in path, teacher_id (person_id) in body. Coordinator must manage that major."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Programs Teacher",
      "description": "Teacher can list students enrolled in courses they teach.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Course Students",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/programs/teacher/courses/1/students/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "programs", "teacher", "courses", "1", "students", ""]},
            "description": "Returns students enrolled in the course offering's cohort. Teacher must be assigned to that offering. Replace 1 with offering_id. Response: { students: [{ person_id, full_name, email, student_number }] }."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Registration Coordinator",
      "description": "Major coordinator (MajorCoordinator) can list pending submissions for their major(s), accept (final stage) or reject (session deleted). Requires auth as a user whose Person is a MajorCoordinator for the session's major.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "List Pending",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/coordinator/pending/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "coordinator", "pending", ""]},
            "description": "Returns sessions with status SUBMITTED for majors the current user coordinates. Response: { sessions: [{ session_id, person_id, full_name, email, base_role, payload, created_at }] }."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Accept",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/coordinator/1/accept/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "coordinator", "1", "accept", ""]},
            "description": "POST with session_id in path. Sets session status to ACCEPTED (final stage). Only coordinator for that major."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Reject",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/coordinator/1/reject/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "coordinator", "1", "reject", ""]},
            "description": "POST with session_id in path. Deletes the registration session. Only coordinator for that major."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Registration test path - Student",
      "description": "Run these in order to test full student path (no internship, not working): 1 Login, 2 Get State, 3–6 Answer steps, 7 Submit. Uses {{email}}/{{password}}; create test user first if needed.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Login",
          "request": {
            "auth": {"type": "noauth"},
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{email}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{password}}\"\n}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/auth/login/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "auth", "login", ""]},
            "event": [{"listen": "test", "script": {"exec": ["if (pm.response.code !== 200) return;", "var d = pm.response.json();", "if (d.access_token) pm.collectionVariables.set(\"access_token\", d.access_token);", "if (d.refresh_token) pm.collectionVariables.set(\"refresh_token\", d.refresh_token);"], "type": "text/javascript"}}]
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Get state",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/state/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "state", ""]}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Answer Q1 student",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"finished_master\": false\n}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "4. Answer student_data",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"student_data\": {\n    \"major_id\": 1,\n    \"student_number\": \"M2-2024-001\",\n    \"cohort_year\": \"2024\"\n  }\n}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "5. Answer has_internship false",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"has_internship\": false\n}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "6. Answer is_working false",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"is_working\": false\n}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/answer/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "answer", ""]}
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "7. Submit",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {"mode": "raw", "raw": "{}"},
            "url": {"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/v1/registration/submit/", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "registration", "submit", ""]}
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
